108
0:04:45.117,000 --> 0:04:47,000
but interestingly, if you were watching it live,

109
0:04:48,000 --> 0:04:5,000
there was this suspense that built

110
0:04:50.631,000 --> 0:04:52,000
because the actual tweets,

