0:05:20.813,000 --> 0:05:22,000
It began with this tweet: "On November 28

122
0:05:23.443,000 --> 0:05:25,000
at 10:13 p.m.,

123
0:05:25.594,000 --> 0:05:27,000
a woman identified as Miranda Brown,

124
0:05:27.669,000 --> 0:05:29,000
44, of Brooklyn, fell to her death

125
0:05:30.499,000 --> 0:05:32,000
