132
0:05:47.16,000 --> 0:05:5,000
leading up to this moment at 10:13 p.m.

133
0:05:50.285,000 --> 0:05:52,000
when this woman falls to her death.

134
0:05:52.563,000 --> 0:05:55,000
These three characters brought an authentic vision

135
0:05:55.667,000 --> 0:05:56,000
from multiple perspectives.

136
0:05:57.389,000 --> 0:05:59,000
One reviewer called Elliott's story

137
0:05:59.715,000 --> 0:06:01,000
"Twitter fiction done right," because she did.

138
0:06:02.605,000 --> 0:06:03,000
She captured that voice

139
0:06:04.333,000 --> 0:06:07,000
